From: Andrew Morton <>
Subject: Re: [Bug 492] New: Zip drive parallel-port driver causes segfault in 2.5.x
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
